Reasoning: 
1. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - This paper focuses on spiking neural networks and their training, which falls under the scope of neural computing. 
2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper uses image classification datasets to evaluate the proposed method, indicating a focus on computer vision tasks. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new method for training deep neural networks, which falls under the scope of machine learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a new method for training artificial neural networks, which falls under the scope of artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the implementation of spiking neural networks on neuromorphic processors, which falls under the scope of systems and control.
